        "setup": "Create or manage an OAuth client from [OAuth client registration](https://www.meetup.com/api/oauth/create/) / [OAuth Clients](https://www.meetup.com/api/oauth/list/). Meetup says only members with an active [Meetup Pro subscription](https://www.meetup.com/pro) can create new OAuth consumers, and approval is not guaranteed. Register a `redirect_uri`, then use Meetup's OAuth 2 flows from the [authentication docs](https://www.meetup.com/graphql/authentication/) to obtain an access token sent as `Authorization: bearer {ACCESS_TOKEN}`. The docs also describe server flow, refresh-token flow, and a JWT flow for server-to-server use.",
